resources.string: An organization that operates in providing education and inviting all parties to support and preserve the natural environment and support creative waste management
Realizing a sustainable and harmonious natural environment through the active participation of the entire community in efforts to preserve and protect nature.

Providing comprehensive educational programs to increase public awareness of the importance of protecting and preserving the environment, Carrying out extensive campaigns to invite the public to participate in real actions that support environmental sustainability, Forming partnerships with various parties, including the government, private sector and local communities to work together together to develop sustainable solutions to environmental problems.
